    "Statistical significance was established at a p-value of less than 0.05, ensuring a comprehensive and rigorous evaluation of the study's findings.",
    "Statistical analyses were performed using Prism (version 10.3.0) and ChatGPT-4 (OpenAI, San Francisco, California, USA).",
